{"tid":1418342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住呢場仗，贏咗先可以救返曬所有人出嚟。","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:44:15.000Z","uid":43785,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39162cff04d28f57731596e7e9a440a68f7bcc26","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:28:03.000Z","msg":"好多人為香港貢獻咗自己嘅前途， 我哋依家係用上香港嘅前途去救番義士嘅前途。 <br />\n相反若果呢場仗輸咗嘅話， 香港人一定會被清算， 香港嘅前途同義士嘅前途都冇晒架啦！<br />\n<br />\n記住呢場仗， 由開始嘅一刻已經返唔到轉頭，註定係贏咗先可以救返曬所有人出嚟。<br />\n所有人出唔到嚟， 唔係因為唔得，而係因為我哋未贏。 因為林鄭月娥未答應香港市民五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n當林鄭月娥同習近平答應我哋五大訴求嘅時候。<br />\n所有義士都可以放返曬出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n記住不要絕望， 更不要放棄希望<br />\n看似好遙遠，但我哋其實只差一步<br />\n「五大訴求， 缺一不可」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"210becdc0d02c5e2f427b88c961ee4af45a5c2e4","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:30:36.000Z","msg":"記住呢一個群組活動冇大台， 冇人會走出去認輸。<br />\n<br />\n你除非拉走曬200萬香港人 ，否則我地係注定唔會失敗。我哋只不過係未成功！"},{"pid":"424ea26f692a2e1ceee91865db4171029f885962","tid":1418342,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:31:21.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dwROzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dwROzT</a>"},{"pid":"ea81809849366691fc633e9518ef96694fe758bc","tid":1418342,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:31:28.000Z","msg":"今日呀叔講大家搞事，好易出事，我忍撚住唔出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416443</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4bece3ec5e556b30cba5f2862a79478d2d6ee4b","tid":1418342,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:32:25.000Z","msg":"我地唔可以輸 <br />\n輸左一定比支共清算屠城 今日新疆 明日香港呀！"},{"pid":"8c1668bfd37eaef99eec67066b0f4e985cd2604d","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:37:37.000Z","msg":"我哋今日雖然未令林鄭月娥跪低。<br />\n<br />\n但一定會為今後抗爭引起蝴蝶效應， 冇人會諗到陳同佳會搞到咁大單嘢。<br />\n<br />\n更加冇人會諗到元朗嗰單嘢會激起更多人支持我地。<br />\n<br />\n暫時不要散播負面住！<br />\n聽朝仲有輿論戰要打， 集中屌黑社會嗰度。<br />\n中聯辦再搵刀手同黑社會斬人"},{"pid":"ca14994cd5e7c3e3a4f00dc36cadb10c46591813","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4bece3ec5e556b30cba5f2862a79478d2d6ee4b","tid":1418342,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:32:25.000Z","msg":"我地唔可以輸 <br />\n輸左一定比支共清算屠城 今日新疆 明日香港呀！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:38:58.000Z","msg":"冇錯， 我哋唔可以認輸<br />\n輸咗嘅話，等於輸咗個香港， 輸曬所有位香港抗爭個嘅義士，輸埋我哋下一代生活嘅地方。"},{"pid":"ec9720ded99e26d2827af23b37218f7b99b82d28","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8045edd97f743fee97089ad3e7fff6d883eac8","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:20:32.000Z","msg":"記住要救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe1a087e0a090997e05c05bd6fe977fd646ccb4","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1e5236d843842696c70c6b4bdfdfcdf8288bf3","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:26:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"644541a76e13c0f0665110d8365a55b83e2e080b","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:40:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5934e020766f5f96df3c68c6f6677999885eee8d","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08567a837c760e49e0e28215d7492da05907cab3","tid":1418342,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}